OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy with the odd
OL,6,Flight shower in the morning. Drier for
OL,7,Fa time around the middle of the day
OL,8,Fbefore more persistent rain spreads
OL,9,Feast through the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight with mainly
OL,13,Flight rain, but this will turn heavier
OL,14,Fand more persistent at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FIt will be cloudy throughout
OL,17,Fthe day with light rain or drizzle,
OL,18,Fbut this becoming persistent and heavy
OL,19,Fat times. Breezy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
